channel.title: Chache Help
channel.description:
[size=11pt]Hey, im haveing some Chache trouble with my 317. What im trying to do is change the skill button. I changed it in skillnew and skill602. and i just dont know why it wont change..[/size] Like so.... [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2zszihw.png[/img]
i Changed it in interfaces, skillnew and skill602 Like this.. [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/14mykgi.png[/img]
But i still end up with this... [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2zszihw.png[/img]
If anyone knows why could you please help me? it would be highly appreciated Thanks for reading - Kush

item.title: Chache Help
item.dc:creator: @Onix Onix
item.description:
@Onix wrote:

Check that the client is loading that sprite from the file and not from the cache inside the actual cache. Also make sure you restart your client after changing it.
